Sonova’s Rihs Bought Back Shares, SonntagsZeitung Reports

-- B y   E l e n a   L o g u t e n k o v a
-- 
2011-04-03T10:47:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-03/sonova-s-rihs-bought-back-shares-sonntagszeitung-reports.html
Sonova Holding AG (SOON) ’s former Chairman,
Andy Rihs, bought back shares at the same price he sold them
before the company’s profit warning last month, he told
 SonntagsZeitung  in an interview.  Rihs told the newspaper that he gave green light for the
share sale “weeks” before it took place on March 8, while
sales data for February was sent to the members of the board of
directors on March 10.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elena Logutenkova in Zurich at 
 elogutenkova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net  